What are you doing? In a place like this...
Whoa!!! W-Who is it?! Oh, it's Konoha!
Hey... why are the bandits here?!

Ahaha! It's nothing, really! I just finished
beating them up just now!

Hey, what's going on?! You didn't just set us up,
did you?

Konoha, it's not like that. There are various
things, you know. The world of adults...

Sigh... Baretta, it's fine already. I understand.
So all of you over there, I'll let you off the
hook today, so hurry up and get out of here.
Baretta has something to talk about.

Do as Konoha says and disperse for today. Or do
you all want to be unable to go home?

So, you're a Devil Witch, huh? I heard everything
from Freya.

I was asked to save you... With this Flame of
Repentance, I can save you.

Return to being a magical girl and fight demons
with everyone...

I won't go back to being a magical girl. That weak
power is meaningless.

In this state, life has become easier. I'm doing
my job at the guild properly, so there shouldn't
be any problem.

What are you saying? Even if things seem fine now,
if your heart is completely corrupted, it will be
the end! I mean, you were plotting with the
Bandits, right? You were planning to break the
barrier pillar or something like that, right?

Shut up! Shut up shut up shut up!!! Then prove it,
show me the power of your magical girl!

If you're saying that your magical girl is
stronger than our Devil Witch, then I'll use that
Flame of Repentance on you as a punishment.

I don't understand this, but it's fine. Baretta, I
will defeat you and definitely return you to your
original magical girl form...

Hmph... You're such an annoying newcomer. Don't
regret it later!

Kaha... U, it can't be... No way... I won't let
myself be caught off guard...
Well... I win... I'll use the Flame of Repentance.

Geez, that Frya... How long is she going to take
care of me, damn witch... Damn witch...

Haa... haa... This is... the Flame of
Repentance... Indeed, it feels like the haze in my
mind has cleared...

Are you okay? It seems like your appearance hasn't
changed, but...

Appearance? Ah, I see. Normally, you can't see it,
thanks to being a Devil Witch, Konoha. Somehow, I
feel refreshed.

I'm glad... With this, everything will be fine. I
won't let those Bandits come up with any strange
schemes anymore.

Bandits? Did I do something like that! Oh no, oh
no! From now on, I have to be serious.

I'll go talk to Frya for a moment, Konoha. I've
caused you a lot of trouble.
I'm fine, I think Frya will be happy too.
Ah, I see. I also need to report to Frya once.

For now, I'm glad. It seems like Baretta will be
serious about being a magical girl from now on.

Kaha... Ugh, that's right... I can't believe... I
let my guard down...

Now... I win... I'll use the flames of
retribution.

Tch... I guess there's no other choice... Lend me
that flame of retribution or whatever. I'll do it
myself...

As I thought, Konoha has also fallen into
corruption! Ahahaha! Burning, burning!

No wonder you're strong. With this, the difference
in power is clear!

Sorry, but it's naive to think that only I will be
purified! Now, I may have let my guard down
earlier, but it won't happen again.

No way...! Is this how I'm going to lose...?! It
can't be...

Baretta... You've made Frya's feelings go to
waste...

I said before that you helped me in the past, so
this time Frya was just trying to help you.

Frya's hope was to save you, but now, the flames
of retribution are gone...
There is only one way to save you.
No... please stop... I don't want Konoha to die...

I'm sorry, but please stop...! I knew this might
happen...

Baretta, even if it takes some time, would it be
alright if I search for another way?
Why do you care so much about me?

Of course! Because she's my savior... I'm sorry,
Konoha. I was about to make you feel uncomfortable
soon.

No, I... I'm sorry for keeping it a secret that I
had fallen into depravity.

I thought we had to use it on one person, so this
should be fine.

Baretta, temporarily leave the guild and come to
me. I will help you control and suppress your
descent into depravity, even if it's just a
little.

Mmm... I guess there's no other choice. I can't
say anything this time.

Konoha, please come to my house again once you've
calmed down.

There's no way I can make it with such weak power
compared to the Devil Witch and the Magical Girl.

Geez, that Flya, always causing trouble... Such a
bothersome witch...

I didn't want to do it, but it seems like it's
time to give her the final blow. We don't need
outdated witches like her in this world anymore.
Hahaha! Too bad, Konoha. I won this time.

Geez, that Flya, always causing trouble... Such a
bothersome witch...

I didn't want to do it, but it seems like it's
time to give her the final blow. We don't need
outdated witches like her in this world anymore.
